A Resources A.1 Python scikit-learn A.2 Machine learning data set repositories A.2.1 MLDATA mldata.org This repository manages the following types of objects: Data Sets - Raw data as a collection of similarily structured objects. Material and Methods - Descriptions of the computational pipeline. Learning Tasks - Learning tasks defined on raw data. Challenges - Collections of tasks which have a particular theme.
